        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Storing CO2 And Lowering Emissions Act or the SCALE Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes programs within the Department of Energy that provide financial support and incentives to develop infrastructure for carbon dioxide capture, transport, utilization, and storage. </p>]]>
        </text>
